{"tid":1487871,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國工黨暗示BNO平權要先問准中國，國會外交主席對言論表示遺憾","createTime":"2019-08-19T12:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T00:33:34.000Z","uid":305299,"like":16,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"1c40444d540226d953711338fdb93578509bace5","tid":1487871,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"話說上個禮拜英國國會下議院外交委員會主席，保守黨嘅 Tom Tugendhat，一而再，再而三咁發表支持 BNO 平權嘅言論，甚至喺 twitter 上面直接反駁中國，話 BNO 平權係英國國會嘅主權，唔關其他人事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但在野工黨影子財相 John McDonnell 今日早上去 BBC Radio 4 電台接受訪問。主持人問到，工黨喺香港最近嘅示威事情上好似無咩表態，而且又問及對於 Tom Tugendhat 關於平權嘅提議有咩睇法，佢暗示依家離需要平權嘅危險情況仲未有耐 (miles away) ，但佢又無話唔可以平權，佢表示英國政府依家應該要做嘅係去同中國傾，去呼籲中國遵守《中英聯合聲明》<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而保守黨嘅 Tom Tugendhat 事後分別喺facebook 同 twitter 發文，指對於工黨 John McDonnell 唔支持 BNO 平權嘅言論表示遺憾，認為任何人想領導英國，都需要為土本同海外嘅所有英國國民站起來 (stand up) <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順帶講講，其實依位工黨議員 John McDonnell 喺 2015年個陣，係英國國會辯論當時嘅預算案期間，突然喺衫袋到變出一本紅當當嘅《毛主席語錄》出來，引述毛澤東嘅說話來諷刺當時都好親中嘅財相 George Osborne ，依家睇翻，依位工黨議員會唔會其實係地下黨黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後提一提，依到有份英國國會 BNO 平權聯署，大家去幫手簽個名，唔好人地外交委員會主席都出到聲，而我地反而就咩都唔做 (去到9月20號): <a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46zQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=ae9bc386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n===== 傳送門s =====<br />\nBBC 電台訪問 (2:18:58 開始) : <a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/play/m0007q9m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsounds%2Fplay%2Fm0007q9m&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46zQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=737eabc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/play/m0007q9m</a><br />\n<br />\n保守黨嘅 Tom Tugendhat 嘅 facebook 發文: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tomtugendhat/posts/1275871935920776\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftomtugendhat%2Fposts%2F1275871935920776&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46zQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=3cc9e7a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tomtugendhat/posts/1275871935920776</a><br />\n<br />\n保守黨嘅 Tom Tugendhat 嘅 twitter 發文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TomTugendhat/status/1163350598592421888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTomTugendhat%2Fstatus%2F1163350598592421888&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46zQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=fd2853a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTomTugendhat%2Fstatus%2F1163350598592421888&h=dc89d858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TomTugendhat/status/1163350598592421888</a><br />\n<br />\nBBC 中文報導: 《英國影子財相讀毛主席語錄教訓財政大臣》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk/2015/11/151125_uk_parliament_mao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk%2F2015%2F11%2F151125_uk_parliament_mao&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46zQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=f01a7083\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk%2F2015%2F11%2F151125_uk_parliament_mao&h=0786db12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk/2015/11/151125_uk_parliament_mao</a><br />\n<br />\n中方嬲嬲BNO平權建議，英議員：屬英國國會主權，與他人無關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1476236/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1476236/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"b057c3d13ca361871f8e179d00d46e96f3a5418f","tid":1487871,"uid":58552,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:29:57.000Z","msg":"入滲哂"},{"pid":"5e79481dc87900507c4560bc90cd2a7054e79ce3","tid":1487871,"uid":